# Callings: Character Motivation

Before you decide what your character *does*, decide who they *are*. Your calling represents the fundamental drive that compels you to adventure—the psychological truth at your core.

## Understanding Callings

Every calling provides three interconnected elements:

**Flow Benefit** - A mechanical trigger that generates Flow when you act according to your nature

**Narrative Permission** - A special ability that emerges from your calling's unique perspective

**Calling Equipment** - A unique item earned through play that manifests your calling in the world

Together, these elements ensure your calling isn't just background—it actively shapes how you play.

